Plot: Director Michael Apted revisits the same group of British-born adults after a 7 year wait. The subjects are interviewed as to the changes that have occurred in their lives during the last seven years.
Title: 56 Up
Actors: Michael Apted, Bruce Balden, Jacqueline Bassett, Symon Basterfield
tomatoConsensus: Director Michael Apted continues to utilize cinema as a window into the lives of everyday people, and in the reflection of this documentary we can glimpse our own aging humanity.
